      "content": "that works. to really hammer home the \"social decay\" and make the setting feel like it's part of a specific community, can you add some more specific details? maybe describe the types of shops or businesses on these streets, and even mention some of the slang or the specific \"look\" of the people in this district to make it feel less generic? i want to capture that particular cultural vibe that usually defines these kinds of high-crime urban areas.",
